<l>kuṟumaiyu neṭumaiyu maḷaviṟ kōṭaliṟ</l>
<l>ṟoṭarmoḻi yellā neṭṭeḻut tiyala</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As shortness and length [of vowels] are defined</l>
<l>by measure of quantity, all polysyllabic words</l>
<l>are of the nature of long [monosyllables].</l>
      </lg>
